<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFKephart1922">Kephart, Horace (1922). <i>Our Southern Highlanders</i> (New and revised edition ed.). Macmillan. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0870492039" class="internal">ISBN 0-87049-203-9</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Our+Southern+Highlanders&amp;rft.aulast=Kephart&amp;rft.aufirst=Horace&amp;rft.au=Kephart%2C+Horace&amp;rft.date=1922&amp;rft.edition=New+and+revised+edition&amp;rft.pub=Macmillan&amp;rft.isbn=0-87049-203-9&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Appalachia"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li>Light, Melanie and Ken Light (2006). <i>Coal Hollow</i>. Berkeley: University of California Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780520246546" class="internal">ISBN 978-0520246546</a></li>
<li>Olson, Ted (1998). <i>Blue Ridge Folklife</i>. University Press of Mississippi. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1578060230" class="internal">ISBN 1-57806-023-0</a></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFSarnoff2003">Sarnoff, Susan (2003). "<a href="http://www.journalofpoverty.org/JOPABS/JPOABS21.HTM" class="external text" title="http://www.journalofpoverty.org/JOPABS/JPOABS21.HTM" rel="nofollow">Central Appalachia – Still the Other America</a>". <i>Journal of Poverty</i> (The Haworth Press) <b>Volume 7</b> (1 &amp; 2): 123–139. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1300%2FJ134v07n01_06" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1300%2FJ134v07n01_06" rel="nofollow">10.1300/J134v07n01_06</a></span><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.journalofpoverty.org/JOPABS/JPOABS21.HTM" class="external free" title="http://www.journalofpoverty.org/JOPABS/JPOABS21.HTM" rel="nofollow">http://www.journalofpoverty.org/JOPABS/JPOABS21.HTM</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Central+Appalachia+%E2%80%93+Still+the+Other+America&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+Poverty&amp;rft.aulast=Sarnoff&amp;rft.aufirst=Susan&amp;rft.au=Sarnoff%2C+Susan&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.volume=Volume+7&amp;rft.issue=1+%26+2&amp;rft.pages=123%E2%80%93139&amp;rft.pub=The+Haworth+Press&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1300%2FJ134v07n01_06&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.journalofpoverty.org%2FJOPABS%2FJPOABS21.HTM&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Appalachia"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
